This package includes scripts and resource files to allow shared use 
of D. Rubin's code to simulate WFIRST.

If the code has not yet been installed, follow the instructions in "README.install".
To run interactively, see "README.run" in subdirectory "work".
To run as a batch job, see "README.batch" in subdirectory "work".

2017 Dec 4
D. Rabinowitz :  Latest version running on Yale HEP computers
